{"tid":1429040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[天涯歌女] Lia一句話真心稱讚 ITZY彩領《一周偶像》淚崩：很難過","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:09:45.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ac82ec024f82145da322ac0ce9820c9753757d","tid":1429040,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"南韓「怪物新人」ITZY於2月出道，相隔短短5個月，她們再度帶著新曲《ICY》回歸樂壇，7日出演節目《一周偶像》，彩領聽見Lia充滿真心的稱讚，無預警淚灑攝影棚，展現出ITZY幾位成員深厚的友誼，卻也看得粉絲心疼不已，留言安慰「不要哭」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4290/d4290839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4290%2Fd4290839.jpg&h=4b56188a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼彩領聽到Lia的稱暫反而哭了。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4290/d4290837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4290%2Fd4290837.jpg&h=5edc0ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nITZY於7日出演節目《一周偶像》，主持人請她們發自內心真心地稱讚彩領，希望藉此看到她收到稱讚的反應，沒想到，Lia摸著她的頭，用溫暖的語氣說著「彩領啊，妳是很珍貴的孩子」，彩領因為太過感動、眼眶泛紅，接著，Lia抱著她喊「妳很美麗」，自己也無預警跟著哭了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4290/d4290840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4290%2Fd4290840.jpg&h=30786e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼ITZY也紛紛紅了眼眶。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4290/d4290841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4290%2Fd4290841.jpg&h=fcd26ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預料之外的發展，彩領、Lia哭成一片，成員也逐漸紅了眼眶，主持人嚇壞直呼：「成員間感情真的很好。」彩領解釋「因為覺得難過」，她平時也會向對方訴說煩惱，因此更能感受到Lia的真心，她一時忍不住豐富情感哭了。這段播岀後，也讓粉絲更暸解她們的革命情感。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MG338lECMYI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMG338lECMYI&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=8bf51790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MG338lECMYI</a>"},{"pid":"5b57e42b6359578b315a2268961b6f16b607e684","tid":1429040,"uid":7878,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNZEvfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNZEvfZ.jpg&h=e5405a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c5fe14b94d6227cb012505f59ea4860d8cf2b1c","tid":1429040,"uid":136738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"ok 我唔反lia了！！！"},{"pid":"f0a6e78e6cbaa0af21fbe42f70950ffc79d743f3","tid":1429040,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b57e42b6359578b315a2268961b6f16b607e684","tid":1429040,"uid":7878,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNZEvfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNZEvfZ.jpg&h=e5405a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbcbdf7063ed9cfddfef2f04fbabf0a1aa97b42","tid":1429040,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">不要傷害我的孩子</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc5a430204a09d50741cf41ed69747c75df0d4e3","tid":1429040,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbcbdf7063ed9cfddfef2f04fbabf0a1aa97b42","tid":1429040,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">不要傷害我的孩子</div></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gi